# Types of Growth
      Curves..
      Büyüme Türleri (Fonksiyonları)
      https://jamesclear.com/growth-curves

# Exponential Growth: Improvements come slowly in the beginning (lag phase), but your gains increase rapidly over time. (exponential phase),  and then (stationary phase)... and death...
                        Requires patience to get past the early period and see results.
      (unrestricted)

      Formula: f(x)=2^x

            y
            |
            |
            |
Population  |
  Results   |
   Size     |
            |
            |
            |________________________________ x
                         Time / Effort

            Example: Bacterial Growth Curve..

# Logarithmic Growth: Improvements come quickly in the beginning, but your gains decrease overtime.
                        Requires consistency even when you see a slowdown in wins.


# Logistic Growth: Carrying capacity (K) of environment
            (restricted)
            

